      <div class="faq">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Can I get a refund?</h4>
            <p>Yes, full refunds are available until April 1, 2026. After that, tickets can be transferred to another person.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Do you offer student discounts?</h4>
            <p>Yes! Our Community ticket tier is available for students, non-profits, and open-source contributors.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Can I transfer my ticket?</h4>
            <p>Yes, tickets can be transferred to another person at any time before the event.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Is VAT included in the price?</h4>
            <p>No, prices shown are excluding VAT. Dutch VAT (21%) will be added at checkout.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Will there be dietary options?</h4>
            <p>Yes, we'll accommodate vegetarian, vegan, and other dietary requirements. You can specify these during registration.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
